{
  "texts": [
    "Moreover, Bai et al. (2022) investigated the impact of green finance on carbon emissions, revealing a complex relationship influenced by economic structure and regional differences.",
    "Their findings show that green finance has been particularly effective in reducing emissions in the more industrialized eastern regions of China.",
    "This aligns with the broader objective of SDG 13 to reduce emissions and combat climate change but also highlights the need for region-specific policies to ensure that green finance can effectively drive down emissions across diverse economic contexts.",
    "Finally, Li et al. (2022) examine the broader implications of green finance in transitioning to a low-carbon economy.",
    "They find that while green finance significantly aids this transition, its effectiveness diminishes without the support of low-carbon technological innovations."
  ]
}